{
  "stem": "27340.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't remember its exact surrounding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we would, in fact, spend the evening and ultimately the night there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We would never sleep because these people would talk to us, imbue us with their plans, with their enthusiasm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were personalities of an-- of an outstanding sort of-- outstanding personalities, and they imbued us with a lot of enthusiasm.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then at weekends, we had our own group meetings, again, and so that's where we imparted that enthusiasm to our numbers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was a fantastic experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was always in groups, and they were psychologically very, very capable, I think.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They never singled out a specific individual.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, an individual never established a very-- to my knowledge, at least, and certainly I never developed, or given the opportunity to develop, a very personal relationship with any one of them.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Possibly for security, secondly because their concept was, after all, have a youth team operation, teamwork, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on that basis, no, I don't have any-- any very specific sort of the reminiscences of any-- any-- any-- any particular relationship.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But certainly, they knew my face.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Certainly, I knew them, because the whole world knew them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But just to be in their company and to listen to what, in fact, their plans were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What they-- obviously, they were not plans that were considered to be secret in any way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They wouldn't divulge that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But just to talk about the whole concept, the liberation, the ideas that one had and what one would do with a country or one's own, and so on, was, you know, incredibly inspiring.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the full hog, in so far that I then went on a kibbutz Hachshara.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
